#: ../../../release_details/9.4/fix-deserialization-bug-in-vtkCollection.md:1
msgid "Fix deserialization bug in vtkCollection"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/fix-deserialization-bug-in-vtkCollection.md:3
msgid ""
"Fixes a bug in the deserialization of `vtkRenderer`. When an actor in a "
"renderer was replaced with another actor, and the scene reserialized with "
"`vtkObjectManager`, the deserializer was unable to detect that the actor had "
"changed. Instead, the renderer continued to show the old actor. This bug in "
"deserialization of vtkCollection is now fixed."
msgstr ""
